==English==
===Noun===
'''sweet pepper''' (''Plural:'' '''sweet peppers''')

#The fruit of a non-spicy variety of [[pepper]] ([[genus]] ''[[Capsicum]]''), also called [[bell pepper]].  Available in green, red, yellow and orange skinned varieties (the green is generally the unripe variety and the colored versions the sweeter, ripe fruit).

===Usage notes===
*In Britain these are known as [[green pepper]]s, [[yellow pepper]]s and [[red pepper]]s